{"\"Invalid attempt to destructure non-iterable instance.\\nIn order to be iterable, non-array objects must have a [Symbol.iterator]() method.\"":"E0","'Arrays must have the same length'":"E1","'string notation required for auto precision.'":"E2","INPUT_ERROR":"E3","FINALIZE_ERROR":"E4","'Illegal argument ' + message":"E5","'Invalid data'":"E6","'The amount of data is too big to be stored in a QR Code'":"E7","'\\n' +\n      'The chosen QR Code version cannot contain this amount of data.\\n' +\n      'Minimum version required to store current data is: ' + bestVersion + '.\\n'":"E8","'No input text'":"E9","'Encoder not initialized'":"E10","'\"' + data + '\"' +\n      ' cannot be encoded with mode ' + Mode.toString(mode) +\n      '.\\n Suggested mode is: ' + Mode.toString(bestMode)":"E11","'\"version\" cannot be null or undefined'":"E12","'\"version\" should be in range from 1 to 40'":"E13","'\"toSJISFunc\" is not a valid function.'":"E14","'Invalid QR Code version'":"E15","'FetchError'":"E16","`HTTP error! status: ${response.status}`":"E17","'Invalid JSON response from server'":"E18","'The provider is not valid.'":"E19","'Network response was not ok'":"E20"}